- OK.

288
00:16:42,729 --> 00:16:44,931
Don't you worry
about your thing.

289
00:16:44,964 --> 00:16:46,398
Alright, you go tell her.

290
00:16:46,431 --> 00:16:47,432
EVA: (on phone)
<i>I love you, daddy.</i>

291
00:16:47,466 --> 00:16:48,533
