00:29:10,342 --> 00:29:12,511
Spy novels?

504
00:29:12,544 --> 00:29:14,113
I'm just doing research.

505
00:29:14,146 --> 00:29:15,581
On women in swimming pools?

506
00:29:18,317 --> 00:29:21,120
It's good you quick,
