1113
01:02:58,070 --> 01:03:00,372
Everything I could remember.

1114
01:03:00,406 --> 01:03:05,978
The name of associates
and accomplices.

1115
01:03:06,011 --> 01:03:07,446
They wanted me to write
everything down

1116
01:03:07,479 --> 01:03:09,148
