the car gave to people.

1207
01:08:39,645 --> 01:08:41,948
Freedom is what people wanted.

1208
01:08:41,981 --> 01:08:44,784
Our product wasn't gambling
or the casinos.

1209
01:08:44,817 --> 01:08:47,385
