Son of a bitch.

1225
01:09:39,105 --> 01:09:49,048
(♪♪♪)

1226
01:09:57,924 --> 01:09:58,925
(Sighing)

1227
01:09:58,958 --> 01:10:01,794
Right, so who is that?

1228
